{
  "name": "@hashgraph/smart-contracts",
  "version": "0.4.0-SNAPSHOT",
  "description": "Hedera Smart Contract Service supporting files",
  "scripts": {
    "start": "nodemon mongoServer.js"
  },
  "files": [
    "/contracts/**/*.sol",
    "/contracts/**/**/**/*.sol"
  ],
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "git+https://github.com/hashgraph/hedera-smart-contracts.git"
  },
  "author": "Hedera Smart Contracts Team",
  "license": "Apache-2.0",
  "bugs": {
    "url": "https://github.com/hashgraph/hedera-smart-contracts/issues"
  },
  "homepage": "https://github.com/hashgraph/hedera-smart-contracts#readme",
  "devDependencies": {
    "@hashgraph/hedera-local": "^2.8.0",
    "@nomicfoundation/hardhat-chai-matchers": "^1.0.6",
    "@nomicfoundation/hardhat-network-helpers": "^1.0.8",
    "@openzeppelin/contracts": "^4.9.2",
    "@openzeppelin/contracts-upgradeable": "^4.8.3",
    "@openzeppelin/hardhat-upgrades": "^1.22.1",
    "hardhat": "^2.15.0",
    "mocha": "^10.2.0",
    "mocha-junit-reporter": "^2.2.0",
    "mocha-multi-reporters": "^1.5.1",
    "nodemon": "^2.0.22"
    
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "@hashgraph/sdk": "latest",
    "@nomicfoundation/solidity-analyzer": "^0.1.0",
    "@nomiclabs/hardhat-ethers": "^2.2.3",
    "@nomiclabs/hardhat-etherscan": "^3.1.7",
    "argon2": "^0.30.3",
    "dotenv": "^16.3.1",
    "ejs": "^3.1.9",
    "ethers": "^5.7.2",
    "express": "^4.18.2",
    "hashconnect": "^0.0.6",
    "jsonwebtoken": "^9.0.0",
    "mongodb": "^5.6.0",
    "mongoose": "^7.3.0",
    "multer": "^1.4.5-lts.1",
    "path": "^0.12.7",
    "solc": "^0.8.20"
  }
}
